## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not capture the full scope of climate change impacts on developed countries. The economic impacts are particularly complex and may require more detailed, region-specific studies to understand fully. Additionally, the social and environmental impacts are evolving, and ongoing research is necessary to keep the information current.